comments.content: Looks FF-ish to me, but I can't get in there to check.
It has a few Futura-ish undertones. But that ain't it.
I don't think it's Dax because the R's leg originates too far from the stem. How about Formata Condensed Medium, or FF Scala Sans Bold?

Ok, I see that now. My impulse was to say maybe they compressed it graphically, but then you think I'm cheating.;-)   
   
I see what you mean about the way the corners seem almost rounded, which is why Dax sounded good at first. I'm stuck!
